	\caption{Transport gap versus strain direction $\theta$ for two different $\sigma$ values (a) and versus $\sigma$ for $\theta = 45^\circ$ (b) for zigzag oriented graphene systems. (c) Schematics illustrating the displacement induced by srain along the $k_y$ axis of the Dirac points related to the two graphene domains (see text).}
